# Environment Configuration Example
# Copy this file to .env.local, .env.development, .env.test, etc.

# Specify the application environment
# Options: local, development, test, staging, production
VITE_APP_ENV=local

# The environment setting controls:
# - Navbar background color
# - Default system message on load
# - Message type (info, warning, error, success)
#
# Environment Color Guide:
# - local:       Blue navbar (info)
# - development: Green navbar (success)
# - test:        Yellow navbar (warning)
# - staging:     Orange navbar (warning)
# - production:  Red navbar (error)
